{
  "text": "An unexpected symmetry of the matrix S is the Galois action discussed in [CITATION_1] . For any \u03c3 \u2208 Gal(K r,k /Q ), there exists a permutation \u00b5 \u2192 \u03c3\u00b5 of P r,k",
